# OSINT Content Engine — Full Codebase Analysis & Opinions

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Data Sources"
        G[Google News RSS]
        B[Bing News RSS]
        R[Reddit JSON API]
    end

    subgraph "Ingestion Layer"
        M[main.py — 15min scheduler]
        PS[polite_scraper.py — Trafilatura + curl_cffi]
        BS[bing_scraper.py — RSS parser]
        RS[reddit_scraper.py — JSON API]
    end

    subgraph "AI Layer"
        ZS[BART-MNLI Zero-Shot Filter]
        QW[Qwen 2.5:3b via Ollama — KG Extraction]
    end

    subgraph "Resolution Layer"
        ER[knowledge_graph.py — 2-Layer Gauntlet]
        JW[Jellyfish — Jaro-Winkler]
        SE[all-MiniLM-L6-v2 — Sentence Embeddings]
    end

    subgraph "Storage"
        SQ[(SQLite — tracking.db)]
        N4[(Neo4j — Graph DB)]
    end

    subgraph "Analysis"
        WD[watchdog.py — Tripwire Daemon]
        LB[ai_pipeline.py — Live Briefing Engine]
    end

    subgraph "UI"
        ST[Streamlit Dashboard]
        AG[streamlit-agraph — Visual Link Analysis]
    end

    G --> M
    B --> M
    R --> M
    M --> PS
    M --> BS
    M --> RS
    PS --> ZS
    BS --> ZS
    RS --> ZS
    ZS -->|pass| QW
    ZS -->|junk/low confidence| X[Dropped]
    QW --> ER
    ER --> JW
    ER --> SE
    ER --> N4
    QW --> SQ
    WD --> N4
    WD --> SQ
    ST --> SQ
    ST --> N4
    ST --> LB
    LB --> N4
    LB --> QW
    ST --> AG
```

